---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Teaching"
  description="Matteo Antonini teaches multi-agent AI systems in the Master CESMA program at the University of Rome Tor Vergata."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-12" transition:animate="fade">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Teaching</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none" transition:animate="fade">
      <p>
        I teach a module on multi-agent AI systems in the{' '}
        <a href="https://master-cesma.it/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><strong>Master CESMA</strong></a>{' '}
        program at the University of Rome Tor Vergata. CESMA is a postgraduate program focused on
        AI, data science, and digital transformation.
      </p>

      <h2>What the module covers</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>LLM fundamentals and prompt engineering</li>
        <li>RAG — Retrieval-Augmented Generation</li>
        <li>Agent architecture — instruction, model, tools, state</li>
        <li>Multi-agent patterns — sequential, parallel, loop, supervisor</li>
        <li>Hands-on with Google ADK and real industry use cases</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Course materials</h2>
      <p>
        All materials, notebooks, and code are open source.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>2026 edition</strong> —{' '}
          <a href="https://gitlab.com/cesma/2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            course repository
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>2025 edition</strong> —{' '}
          <a href="https://gitlab.com/cesma/cesma-2025" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            course repository
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
